,30,209,210,211,212,210,213,214,123],"isic003272","fragment of an epitaph",{"_":5},"catina","catania","sicilia","sicily","museo civico di catania","ancient greek",[],{"title":217,"body":218,"divs":219,"editions":246,"images":265,"handnote":271},"ISic003272. Fragment of an Epitaph","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Σ̣ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>Ι \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐ\n                    δεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">οὐ-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[δεὶς]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">[ἀθ]άνατος\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\"> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ] ΙΣΙ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ] Σ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span> Ι \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐδεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">οὐδεὶς\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">ἀθάνατος\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>Ι\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐ\n                    δεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">ΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">..]ΑΝΑΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Σ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span> Ι\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐδεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">ΟΥΔΕΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">ΑΘΑΝΑΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003272_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003272_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003272.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003272-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Korhonen restores οὐ[δεὶς] at l. 2, but it seems there is a space after υ and that the restoration should continue at l. 3\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… Nobody is immortal.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… Nessuno è immortale.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment is part of an epitaph: Korhonen restores a formula found in Greek pagan and Christian inscriptions and in Latin funerary inscriptions (in which it occurs in Greek), \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">οὐδεὶς ἀθάνατος\u003C/span>. The formula is found in another Latin inscription from Catania, CIL 10.7111 = IG 14.513 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000393\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000393\u003C/a>: on the formula, see Marcel Simon, ‘Θάρσει Οὐδεὶς Ἀθάνατος: Étude de Vocabulaire Religieux', Revue de l'histoire des religions 113 (1936): 188–206. The traces at l. 2 are not compatible with \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">εὐψύχ(ε)ι\u003C/span>, which usually accompanies the expression. It is not possible to say whether this is a pagan or a Christian epitaph.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 54.0908 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 159 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp>A with straight bar, lunate Σ, Ο at l. 2 has a mark inside.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  20-25  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[220,223,226,229,232,234,237,240,243],{"id":221,"html":222},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Σ̣ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span>Ι \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐ\n                    δεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">οὐ-\u003Cbr id=\"al3-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[δεὶς]\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">[ἀθ]άνατος\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\"> [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ] ΙΣΙ [\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span> ] Σ \u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.\u003C/span> Ι \u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐδεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">οὐδεὶς\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">ἀθάνατος\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al0-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>].\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span>Ι\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐ\n                    δεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">ΟΥ\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[....\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">..]ΑΝΑΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]Σ\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·\u003C/span> Ι\u003Cspan data-text=\"οὐδεὶς\" data-n=\"45\" data-lemma=\"οὐδείς\">ΟΥΔΕΙΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"ἀθάνατος\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἀθάνατος\">ΑΘΑΝΑΤΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>",{"id":224,"html":225},"facsimile-images","\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003272_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003272_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic003272.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003272-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>",{"id":227,"html":228},"apparatus","\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Korhonen restores οὐ[δεὶς] at l. 2, but it seems there is a space after υ and that the restoration should continue at l. 3\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>",{"id":230,"html":231},"translation","\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… Nobody is immortal.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":230,"html":233},"\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>… Nessuno è immortale.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":235,"html":236},"commentary","\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The fragment is part of an epitaph: Korhonen restores a formula found in Greek pagan and Christian inscriptions and in Latin funerary inscriptions (in which it occurs in Greek), \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">οὐδεὶς ἀθάνατος\u003C/span>. The formula is found in another Latin inscription from Catania, CIL 10.7111 = IG 14.513 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000393\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000393\u003C/a>: on the formula, see Marcel Simon, ‘Θάρσει Οὐδεὶς Ἀθάνατος: Étude de Vocabulaire Religieux', Revue de l'histoire des religions 113 (1936): 188–206. The traces at l. 2 are not compatible with \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">εὐψύχ(ε)ι\u003C/span>, which usually accompanies the expression. It is not possible to say whether this is a pagan or a Christian epitaph.\u003C/p>  ",{"id":238,"html":239},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 54.0908 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 159 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":241,"html":242},"handnote"," \u003Cp>A with straight bar, lunate Σ, Ο at l. 2 has a mark inside.\u003C/p> Lines 1-3  20-25  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":244,"html":245},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[247,249,252,254,257,258,261,262],{"html":248},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":250,"lang":123,"html":251},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al0-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003Cbr id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]ΙΣΙ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\